snippet.title: Season II: Skate Park is Coming to Metaverser!
snippet.description:
Great news! Season 2 of Metaverser is releasing on October 15th, 2022. A Skating area where players will be able to skate around and earn $BABA! You can now purchase your Roller Skates NFT through our shop at the price of 9,000 $BABA. Maximum supply will be only 1,111 NFTs, be an early bird and get yours soon!
#mtvt #gbex #playtoearn
